          <Vi>Danh mục; loại; nhóm</Vi>
          <En>A group or class of people or things that share common characteristics and are classified together.</En>
          <Example>The library organizes books by category, such as fiction, non-fiction, and reference.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
